{"tid":1556864,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［口號撚］香港人 唔係要互相加油啊","createTime":"2019-09-10T01:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T03:24:15.000Z","uid":44367,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7aaf545b7792d34aa0b2bb081005e684bd2a0399","tid":1556864,"uid":44367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:49:29.000Z","msg":"係要你撐身而出 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追究到底</span></span><br />\n否則 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誓不罷休</span></span><br />\n<br />\n繼續煲大所有核彈 721恐襲 831真相 新屋嶺事實 黨鐵出賣港人<br />\n繼續上街 jump 10點高歌 人鏈 連儂牆 以行動表示<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「我係唔會驚架」</span></span><br />\n你有好多野可以做大於淨係「加油」<br />\n以口號展示<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 追究到底 誓不罷休</span></span>既決心<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人<br />\n絕<br />\n不<br />\n罷<br />\n休</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">直至清算曬你班含家產賣港賊高官黑警新移民藍色廢老為止！！！！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"3759fe05e3567cf5780cf67733960a1084cea1a6","tid":1556864,"uid":44367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:53:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誓不罷休</span></span>"},{"pid":"40e696c925586292a8d20db1be3e10dbc0c0f46d","tid":1556864,"uid":44367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:53:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誓不罷休</span></span>"},{"pid":"f52cd72552a8e48a592ffbfad01b2ed4ac11eaa2","tid":1556864,"uid":44367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:53:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誓不罷休</span></span>"},{"pid":"9b391f2c3eb35c69758b629731c260d51681e102","tid":1556864,"uid":44367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl